{
  "stem": "27335.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like in Miskolc, they brought in a professor, a university professor of Miskolc University, who spoke English.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they just left us in the-- in the middle, right in the middle, two chairs, facing like this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he spoke-- spoke to me in English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And turned out to be he was-- he was an employee of the Hungarian Ministry of Agriculture He was sent out to Canada, to Canadian plains to study agriculture, especially with Canadian weed growing and so on.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he knew the place, [NON-ENGLISH], where-- in a place that I-- I that was in my cover story, that-- that I was born in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I was an organizer for a moment in before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I know-- knew the area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I knew the people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and my cover story, that my-- my father was born in-- in [NON-ENGLISH], and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they-- then they took us-- [NON-ENGLISH], the other Canadian-Hungarian and myself, and put us into-- into a-- a motorcycle with the-- with the side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you call them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was sitting in-- on a seat, Mike, sitting on my lap.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there-- there was a-- the driver of the-- the motorcycle, and this-- this officer who was escorting us up to-- up to [NON-ENGLISH], in the-- in the-- in the Buda mountains.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There we-- we found-- we found an English captain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We found a-- a-- a Soviet major and a Romanian lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the two-- two British, and the two of us, there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And well, from that, one by one, we were taken-- taken away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One every day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every day we arrived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "On Friday afternoon, early Friday-- Friday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So Friday, Saturday, Sunday, came Monday.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
